snippet.title: Amber Heard Fan Club
snippet.description:
My name is Yvan Tran of Grand Island, NE. I am a member of National Republican Committee.

The Democratic party under the leadership of Vice-President Kamala Harris over the U.S. border crisis was nothing but a big scheme!

Republican majority leaders are preparing the Articles of Impeachment against President Biden for Treason and Betrayal in Afghanistan. Leaving thousands of U.S. soldiers along with the U.S. Embassy will cost Joe Biden his Presidency title.

The only Governor who can turn around our fragile economy is Ron Desantis, a highly decorated NAVY Lt. COMMANDER from Jacksonville,  FL. A graduate of Harvard and Yale University, who served in Iraq with high distinction and honor. Please, show this valor fighter pilot war hero your support in year 2024. Ron Desantis is the right leader for America where others Presidents have failed.
Vote for Ron Desantis in year 2024. America deserves a smart scholar with Military leadership capabilities.
